      "content": "That makes sense, thank you. It gives them a much more solid footing for the debate. \n\nnow, to help them with the actual round, can you give me a quick summary of the most common rebuttals or counter-arguments that people use against these specific points? specifically the social contract and sovereignty arguments. they need to know what they're up against.",
